registration_responses.description-methods.exclusion-criteria.q:
Participants will be excluded from the study if :
- Participants express suspicions about the procedure during debriefing;
- A technical error occurs or if participants do not fully complete the questionnaire;
- Responses to the verification variables are incorrect;
- The participants are over 25 years old; 
- The attitudes towards increasing tuition fees of the participants is equal to or greater than 4 in the pre-manipulation questionnaire.
